̂̂'''Andahait þis Nikaias''', aiþþau '''''þata nikaiwisko andahait'''''.<br>
Ik galaubja du ainamma Guda, allwaldandin Attin, gaskapjand þis himinis jah þizos airþos, þis allins gasaiƕanins jah unsaiƕanins.<br>
Jah du ainamma Fraujin, Ïesau Xristau, þamma sunau þis Gudis þamma ainabaura, þamma us Attin gabauranin faur allaim aiwam,<br>
Liuhaþ fram liuhaþa, sunjis Guþ fram sunja Guda, gabauran, ni gaskapan, samawist þamma Attin: þairh inei þata allo gaskapan ist.<br>
Izei bi unsis þans mannans jah bi unsarans nasein afiddja fram himina, jah warþ inleikiþs fram Weihamma Ahmin jah Maria Magaþai, jah warþ manna.<br>
Ushramiþs jah faur unsis uf Pauntiu Pilatu, jah wunnans jah gafulhans. Jah urrisans ana þridjin daga þairh þos gameleinins.<br>
Jah atstaig in þaim himinam, sitands ana taihswon þis Attins. Jah aftra qimans miþ wulþau domjands qiwans jah nawins, ƕizei þiudangardi ni habaiþ andi.<br>
Jah du þamma Ahmin þamma Weihin, þamma Fraujin, þamma fram þamma Attin usgagganin,
miþ Attin jah Sunau inweitada jah hauhjada, immei qaþ þairh þans Praufetuns.<br>
Du ainai weihai, gamainjai jah apaustauliskai Aikklesjon.<br>
Andhaita ainai daupeinai bi aflagein frawaurhte.<br>
Beida usstass þize nawe. Jah libain þis anawairþins aiwis.<br><br> 
Amen.
